+
+- **Root cause:** Futures side joined all USDT perpetuals regardless of `status`; spot side already gated on `TRADING`.
+- **Fix (`backend/domain/symbols.py`):** Added `status == "TRADING"` gate on futures leg (mirrors spot filter).
